                是一系列屬性結構};
  更改{如果文件已更改，則將用戶設置為true，
                初始化為false};
 ]不屬性結構是iproperty struct [
    名稱{.startup/.dynamic文件中的變量名};
    值{簡單值};
    註釋{文本註釋如果在文件中存在};
    隱藏{如果在edit屬性gui中不可見的話};
  ];

SetWSDL.en:
Linkage is first applied between the WSDL file and the VTScada modules by generating an XML schema using the WSDL and the parameters provided to this function. The Realm's address is then registered with the VTScada HTTP server to connect the whole thing to the network. Inclusion of the parameter, pResponse is recommended, for the sake of obtaining error messages when debugging. AuthenticationModule, if supplied, must be a subroutine and have the following format: AuthModule(SOAPPackage, pUsername, pPassword, pPrivilege); where: SOAPPackage Is the SOAP payload as an XML node tree pUsername Is a pointer to a variable that the AuthModule should store the username extracted from the SOAP payload. pPassword Is a pointer to a variable that the AuthModule should store the password extracted from the SOAP payload pPrivilege Is a pointer to a variable holding the privilege that the user account must have in order to execute the methods contained in the SOAP payload. The AuthModule must provide a privilege, otherwise the request will be rejected. An example AuthModule might look like the following: ] Authenticate
(
  SOAPPackage { The SOAP payload as an XML node tree };
  pUsername   { Where to store the username };
  pPassword   { Where to store the password };
  pPrivilege  { Where to store a privilege };
)

Authenticate [
If 1;
[
  *pUsername = SOAPPackage\Envelope\Header\TestHeader\#attribs["UserID"];
  *pPassword = SOAPPackage\Envelope\Header\TestHeader\#attribs["Password"];
  *pPrivilege = AppPrivSOAP;
  Return();
]

SetWSDL.zh-cn:
首先使用WSDL文件和VTSCADA模块之间使用链接，并使用WSDL生成XML模式以及提供给此功能的参数。然后，将领域的地址在VTSCADA HTTP服务器上注册，以将整个内容连接到网络。为了在调试时获取错误消息，建议包含参数，建议进行预响应。 AuthenticationModule（如果提供）必须是子例程，并且具有以下格式：AuthModule（Soappackage，Pusername，Passername，ppassword，pprivilege）;地点：SOAPPACKAGE是SOAP有效载荷，作为XML节点树Pusername是一个指向变量的指针，Authmodule应存储从SOAP有效负载中提取的用户名。 ppassword是一个指向变量的指针，Authmodule应将从SOAP有效载荷Pprivilege提取的密码存储是一个指向变量的指针，以持有用户帐户必须具有的特权以执行SOAP Poreload中包含的方法。 Authmodule必须提供特权，否则请求将被拒绝。一个示例authmodule可能看起来如下：]身份验证
（（
  SOAPPACKAGE {SOAP有效负载作为XML节点树};
  pusername {在哪里存储用户名};
  ppassword {在哪里存储密码};
  pprivilege {在哪里存储特权};
）

验证[
如果1;
[
  *pusername = soappackage \ envelope \ header \ testheader \ #attribs [“ userId”];
  *ppassword = soappackage \ envelope \ header \ testheader \ #attribs [“ password”];
  *pprivilege = appprivsoap;
  返回（）;
这是给出的

SetWSDL.zh-tw:
首先使用WSDL文件和VTSCADA模塊之間使用鏈接，並使用WSDL生成XML模式以及提供給此功能的參數。然後，將領域的地址在VTSCADA HTTP服務器上註冊，以將整個內容連接到網絡。為了在調試時獲取錯誤消息，建議包含參數，建議進行預響應。 AuthenticationModule（如果提供）必須是子例程，並且具有以下格式：AuthModule（Soappackage，Pusername，Passername，ppassword，pprivilege）;地點：SOAPPACKAGE是SOAP有效載荷，作為XML節點樹Pusername是一個指向變量的指針，Authmodule應存儲從SOAP有效負載中提取的用戶名。 ppassword是一個指向變量的指針，Authmodule應將從SOAP有效載荷Pprivilege提取的密碼存儲是一個指向變量的指針，以持有用戶帳戶必須具有的特權以執行SOAP Poreload中包含的方法。 Authmodule必須提供特權，否則請求將被拒絕。一個示例authmodule可能看起來如下：]身份驗證
（（
  SOAPPACKAGE {SOAP有效負載作為XML節點樹};
  pusername {在哪裡存儲用戶名};
  ppassword {在哪裡存儲密碼};
  pprivilege {在哪裡存儲特權};
）

驗證[
如果1;
[
  *pusername = soappackage \ envelope \ header \ testheader \ #attribs [“ userId”];
  *ppassword = soappackage \ envelope \ header \ testheader \ #attribs [“ password”];
  *pprivilege = appprivsoap;
  返回（）;
這是給出的

SWrite.en:
If using this function in any code that may write to a USB-to-Serial device, you must make allowances for deficiencies in those devices as follows: the device will ignore everything following the text in the first %s. All text to be written must be in a single parameter passed to a single %s. SWrite(Strm, "%s\r", "AT"); 
  { Only the "AT" is received by a USB-to-Serial device } SWrite(Strm, "%s%s", "AT", \CR); 
  { Only the "AT" is received by a USB-to-Serial device } SWrite(Strm, "%s", Concat("AT", \CR)); 
  { this will succeed if written to a USB-to-Serial device } You cannot write to a read-only file. You may use GetFileAttribs and SetFileAttribs to get/set the read-only attribute. If one of the values to be written is outside of the range of the type indicated by the format specifier, a "0" is written. If the value to be written is invalid, nothing is written for most format specifiers, except for %nb, which will write a "0" in the place of the invalid. Please note that an invalid output does not prevent the execution of the SWrite function. This function returns the number of Vn parameters not written to the stream. A 0 return value indicates success. Variables that contain invalid values that were not written due to their invalidity do not increment this count. An invalid return value indicates an error with one of the parameters. As of version 12.0, VTScada expects all strings to be encoded using UTF-8.

SWrite.zh-cn:
如果在任何可能写入USB到Serial设备的代码中使用此函数，则必须在这些设备中为缺陷提供津贴，如下所示：该设备将忽略第一个％s中的文本之后的所有内容。所有要编写的文本都必须以单个参数传递到单个％s。 swrite（strm，“％s \ r”，“”）; 
  {仅由USB到串行设备收到“ AT”} swrite（strm，“％s％s”，“ at”，\ cr）; 
  {仅由USB到串行设备收到“ AT”} swrite（strm，“％s”，concat（“ at”，\ cr））; 
  {如果写入USB到Serial设备，这将成功}您不能写入只读文件。您可以使用getFileAttribs和setFileatTribs获取/设置仅读取属性。如果要编写的值之一在格式指示符指示的类型范围之外，则写入“ 0”。如果要编写的值无效，则大多数格式指定词没有编写，除了％nb，它将在无效的位置编写“ 0”。请注意，无效的输出不会阻止SWRITE函数的执行。此功能返回未写入流的VN参数的数量。 0返回值表示成功。包含由于无效性而未编写的无效值的变量不会增加此计数。无效的返回值表示其中一个参数的错误。从第12.0版开始，VTSCADA期望使用UTF-8编码所有字符串。

SWrite.zh-tw:
如果在任何可能寫入USB到Serial設備的代碼中使用此函數，則必須在這些設備中為缺陷提供津貼，如下所示：該設備將忽略第一個％s中的文本之後的所有內容。所有要編寫的文本都必須以單個參數傳遞到單個％s。 swrite（strm，“％s \ r”，“”）; 
  {僅由USB到串行設備收到“ AT”} swrite（strm，“％s％s”，“ at”，\ cr）; 
  {僅由USB到串行設備收到“ AT”} swrite（strm，“％s”，concat（“ at”，\ cr））; 
  {如果寫入USB到Serial設備，這將成功}您不能寫入只讀文件。您可以使用getFileAttribs和setFileatTribs獲取/設置僅讀取屬性。如果要編寫的值之一在格式指示符指示的類型範圍之外，則寫入“ 0”。如果要編寫的值無效，則大多數格式指定詞沒有編寫，除了％nb，它將在無效的位置編寫“ 0”。請注意，無效的輸出不會阻止SWRITE函數的執行。此功能返回未寫入流的VN參數的數量。 0返回值表示成功。包含由於無效性而未編寫的無效值的變量不會增加此計數。無效的返回值表示其中一個參數的錯誤。從第12.0版開始，VTSCADA期望使用UTF-8編碼所有字符串。

ThreadHistory.en:
The return value for ThreadHistory is a listing of the last 8192 operations on the thread (max) with five data points per operation. This array should be interpreted in the format, [column][row]. The five rows (data points per operation) are as follows: 0 = Time of execution 1 = Module, State and Statement (type 13) for the operation 2 = State name where the operation is located 3 = Statement number of the operation 4 = Object value for the owning module instance The second parameter is typically populated by using the result of calling ThreadHistory once with an empty array. For example, if you want to obtain the execution history every 5 seconds, you might use the following code to save having to build a 10000-element array every time: If TimeOut(1, 5);
[
  ExecuctionHistory = ThreadHistory(Invalid, ExecutionHistory, 10000);
] The first time the above is called, ExecutionHistory will be Invalid so ThreadHistory will build, populate, and return a multi-dimensional array with 10000 elements. The second time it is called, ExecutionHistory will have been set to the array of the right size / dimensions. ThreadHistory will populate the array it was given and return it, rather than creating a new array.

ThreadHistory.zh-cn:
线程史的返回值是线程（MAX）上最后8192操作的清单，每个操作五个数据点。该数组应以格式解释，[列] [row]。五行（每个操作数据点）如下：0 =执行时间1 =操作的模块，状态和语句（类型13）2 =该操作位置的状态名称3 =操作4 =操作的语句编号4 =对对象值的对象值，其第二个参数通常是通过使用一个空数字的调用线程史的结果来填充第二个参数。例如，如果您想每5秒获取每5秒钟的执行记录，则可以使用以下代码来保存必须每次构建10000个元素数组：如果超时（1，5）;
[
  执行史=线程史（无效，执行史，10000）;
]第一次调用上述情况，执行史将无效，因此线程史将构建，填充和返回具有10000个元素的多维数组。第二次被调用，将执行史将设置为正确的大小 /尺寸的数组。线程史将填充其给出的数组并返回它，而不是创建新数组。

ThreadHistory.zh-tw:
線程史的返回值是線程（MAX）上最後8192操作的清單，每個操作五個數據點。該數組應以格式解釋，[列] [row]。五行（每個操作數據點）如下：0 =執行時間1 =操作的模塊，狀態和語句（類型13）2 =該操作位置的狀態名稱3 =操作4 =操作的語句編號4 =對對象值的對象值，其第二個參數通常是通過使用一個空數字的調用線程史的結果來填充第二個參數。例如，如果您想每5秒獲取每5秒鐘的執行記錄，則可以使用以下代碼來保存必須每次構建10000個元素數組：如果超時（1，5）;
[
  執行史=線程史（無效，執行史，10000）;
]第一次調用上述情況，執行史將無效，因此線程史將構建，填充和返回具有10000個元素的多維數組。第二次被調用，將執行史將設置為正確的大小 /尺寸的數組。線程史將填充其給出的數組並返回它，而不是創建新數組。

WritePropertiesFile.en:
Many properties can be modified with a single call to WritePropertiesFile. The INIFile structure is as follows: INIFiles Struct [
  FileName    { File name to the settings file. Path may be included,
                 but is better specified in the TargetDirectory
                 parameter.                                         };
  OEM         { TRUE if an OEM layer file                             };
  Workstation { Name of the workstation or invalid if global          };
  Layer       { Instance of application layer owning the file         };
  Dynamic     { TRUE if a dynamic property                            };
  Sections    { Dictionary of sections each element of which 
                is an array of Property structures         };
  Changed     { User sets to true if the file has been changed,
                initialized to false                                  };
 ] The INIProperty structure isâ¦ INIProperty Struct [
    Name        { Variable name in the .startup/.dynamic file  };
    Value       { Simple value                                 };
    Comment     { Text comment if present in the file          };
    Hidden      { TRUE if not visible in Edit Properties GUI   };
  ]; Note that if your intention is to write to a configuration file, this function should be called from within a ReadConfiguration callback or a ModifyConfiguration callback.

WritePropertiesFile.zh-cn:
许多属性可以通过单个呼叫来修改WillpropertiesFile。无限结构如下：inifiles struct [
  文件名{文件名到设置文件。可能包括路径，
                 但是在目标界面中更好地指定
                 范围。                                         };
  OEM {true如果OEM层文件};
  工作站{工作站的名称或无效（如果global}};
  层{拥有文件的应用程序层的实例};
  动态{如果动态属性};
  各节{各节词典的每个元素 
                是一系列属性结构};
  更改{如果文件已更改，则将用户设置为true，
                初始化为false};
 ]不属性结构是iproperty struct [
    名称{.startup/.dynamic文件中的变量名};
    值{简单值};
    注释{文本注释如果在文件中存在};
    隐藏{如果在edit属性gui中不可见的话};
  ];请注意，如果您的意图是写入配置文件，则应在ReadConfiguration回调或ModifyConfiguration回调中调用此功能。

WritePropertiesFile.zh-tw:
許多屬性可以通過單個呼叫來修改WillpropertiesFile。無限結構如下：inifiles struct [
  文件名{文件名到設置文件。可能包括路徑，
                 但是在目標界面中更好地指定
                 範圍。                                         };
  OEM {true如果OEM層文件};
  工作站{工作站的名稱或無效（如果global}};
  層{擁有文件的應用程序層的實例};
  動態{如果動態屬性};
  各節{各節詞典的每個元素 
                是一系列屬性結構};
  更改{如果文件已更改，則將用戶設置為true，
                初始化為false};
 ]不屬性結構是iproperty struct [
    名稱{.startup/.dynamic文件中的變量名};
    值{簡單值};
    註釋{文本註釋如果在文件中存在};
    隱藏{如果在edit屬性gui中不可見的話};
  ];請注意，如果您的意圖是寫入配置文件，則應在ReadConfiguration回調或ModifyConfiguration回調中調用此功能。

params.description:
An optional array that specifies what filtering should be applied to socket connections. The order in the ProtocolFilter array determines priority. Each filter item consists of two elements where the first is the filter type ("TLS/SSL", "VIC", "NULL" and "PROXY") The second is a value dependent upon the filter type, noting that there is no second value for "VIC" and "NULL" types.
The certificate subject name is not normally used on a client connection. Examples: For TLS/SSL the value is the subject name in the certificate, given as "CN=host.example.com". For PROXY it is a string. PFilter = New(2);
     PFilter[0] = New(2);
     PFilter[0][0] = "SSL";
     PFilter[0][1] = "CN=host.example.com";
     PFilter[1] = New(2);
     PFilter[1][0] = "NULL";
     PFilter[1][1] = "";

Optional structure, defined as follows: Struct [
    BorderWidth    { Width of left or right border (each), if any  };
    BorderHeight   { Height of top or bottom border (each) , if any};
    TitleBarHeight { Height of titlebar (not including top
                     BorderHeight), if any                         };
  ]; Defaults to a window with a titlebar and thick borders

Optional array. May be used to create additional record fields or modify existing records. A callback subroutine allows record field values to be replaced, for example swapping AccountID for an operator name. If specified, this parameter must be an array that defines the extra record fields. For example: CalculatedFields = New(4);
CalculatedFields[0] = "FriendlyName";
CalculatedFields[1] = "IsActive";
CalculatedFields[2] = "IsUnacked";
CalculatedFields[3] = "IsDisabled";

Optional structure. Array of structures of additional filters. AdditionalFiltersStruct Struct [
 VariableName{ Variable to check };
 OperandID{ See table below for definitions };
 Value{ Value to compare against };
 IsText{ Flag - Do this comparison as text };
 ]; OperandID Meaning 0 Valid 1 True 2 False 3 Less Than 4 Less Than Or Equal 5 Equal (Case sensitive for text) 6 Greater Than Or Equal 7 Greater Than 8 Pattern Match (Not case sensitive for text) Use this to specify a parameter or variable name, the operand to use for the comparison, and a value to compare against.
As an example, the Tag Browser uses this  for the filter to show only tags with Questionable set.

